      "content": "i hear you about the relapse thing but i'm just so hesitant. like, if a doctor sees a patient is 100% asymptomatic, wouldn't a more modern approach just be to stop? i feel like i'm being told to take stuff i don't need. if i'm feeling perfect, can you just confirm that it's okay to stop so i don't have to worry about the side effects for the next week?",
